{"id":2236,"date":"2021-11-12T12:00:20","date_gmt":"2021-11-12T11:00:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/?p=2236"},"modified":"2021-12-15T20:59:17","modified_gmt":"2021-12-15T19:59:17","slug":"ella-sri-lanka","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/ella-sri-lanka\/","title":{"rendered":"Ella, Sri Lanka: 10 Best Things To Do"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in Ella, Sri Lanka<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ella is full of amazing things to do, from hiking the green mountain peaks to jumping in refreshing waterfalls. The town itself has a bustling atmosphere, with plenty of great cafes and restaurants to enjoy after a day in nature. Here are the top things to do while you&#x2019;re in Ella, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/23155430\/beautiful-train-ride-sri-lanka-kandy-ella-best-seat.jpg\" alt=\"beautiful train ride sri lanka kandy ella best seat\" class=\"wp-image-6745\"><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>1. Climb up Little Adam&#x2019;s Peak<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Little Adam&#x2019;s Peak may be smaller than its bigger sibling Adam&#x2019;s Peak, but that doesn&#x2019;t mean it&#x2019;s any less impressive. The stunning ridge is made up of three green peaks that tower above the valley below. Hike through incredible nature, passing through local villages, tea plantations, and long grass fields. Reaching the top is a feeling like no other; it&#x2019;s a chance to take in the sensational, panoramic views and feel as if you&#x2019;re on top of the world!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"293\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-34254 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-300x195.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-600x391.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-800x521.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-1080x704.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-450x293.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-1536x1001.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-163x106.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-276x180.jpg 276w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-768x500.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-1024x667.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-1440x938.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/23114038\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-view-1-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>From Ella Town to the foot of the mountain, it is around a 45-minute walk. From the base to the top, it takes approximately 15 minutes (or 30 minutes to reach the furthest of the 3 peaks).&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>After your beautiful hike, look out for 98 Acres Resort on your return journey. This is a lovely spot to enjoy a coffee or a locally made tea with a view.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Stay in Ella:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/ella-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See all the hotels<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"6587\" class=\"wp-image-6587 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-li