ire his beautiful tea fields. It&#x2019;s also the site where he planted the first seeds of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>&#x2018;s biggest export. It&#x2019;s easy to see why he chose this spot when you look down on the endless green fields of tea, with neat rows of bushes and smiling, hard-working locals picking leaves.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read<\/strong>: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/nuwara-eliya\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best Places to Visit at the Nuwara Eliya Tea Plantations<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Haputale-tuktuk-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"281\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6595 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155626\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Haputale-tuktuk-2.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155626\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Haputale-tuktuk-2-300x187.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155626\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Haputale-tuktuk-2-600x375.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155626\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-L