iv>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Afterward, arrange to take a tour around the local tea factories nearby. Here, you can learn more about the history and production of tea and try it, of course!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/places-to-visit-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Best places to visit in Sri Lanka<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Haputale-locals-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"6585\" class=\"wp-image-6585 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155652\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Haputale-locals-2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155652\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Haputale-locals-2-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155652\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Haputale-locals-2-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155652\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Haputale-locals-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\