r.com\/sri-lanka\/diyaluma-falls-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The 220-meter High Diyaluma Falls near Ella<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-waterfall-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"Diyaluma falls Sri lanka foot\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Diyaluma falls Sri lanka foot\" data-id=\"6617\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-waterfall.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/diyaluma-falls-sri-lanka\/attachment\/sri-lanka-waterfall\/\" class=\"wp-image-6617 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-waterfall-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-waterfall-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-waterfall-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-waterfall-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-waterfall-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-waterfall-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-waterfall-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-waterfall-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155555\/sri-lanka-wat