ce Garden. It&#x2019;s also an excellent opportunity to learn from a local and meet some new people taking part in the course.&#xA0;If that&#x2019;s not available <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/ella-cooking-class-yoga\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">book this popular class in Ella easily online<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Make sure to book in advance because the Ella Spice Garden books up quickly!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/ella-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See all hotels<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2236&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155607\/Things-to-do-ella-sri-lanka-pin.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155607\/Things-to-do-ella-sri-lanka-pin-20x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155607\/Things-to-do-ella-sri-lanka-pin-409x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Ella, Sri Lanka: 10 Best Things To Do\" height=\"600\" width=\"409\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>6. Take a Refreshing Natural Shower at Ravana Falls<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ravana Falls may be smaller than <meta charset=\"utf-8\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/diyaluma-falls-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Diyaluma<\/a>, but it&#x2019;s still jaw-droppingly beautiful. The falls are made up of three tiers, with water cascading between several rock pools, creating the perfect place to swim. Cooling off from the tropical afternoon heat is pure bliss!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s not recommended to climb any further than the first-tier (signs warn you of the dangers), and there are only small muddy trails leading further up the hillside. Additionally, make sure to bring suitable footwear so that you can jump in and out of the pools with ease.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>How to get there:<\/strong> Ravana Falls is just 10 minutes down the winding hill from Ella. You can jump in a tuk-tuk or take the public bus from Ella Town.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ravana-waterfall-2.jpg\" alt=\"Things to do Ella Sri Lanka Ravana waterfall\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Things to do Ella Sri Lanka Ravana waterfall\" class=\"wp-image-6591 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155629\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ravana-waterfall-2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155629\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ravana-waterfall-2-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155629\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ravana-waterfall-2-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155629\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ravana-waterfall-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155629\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ravana-waterfall-2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155629\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ravana-waterfall-2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155629\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ravana-waterfall-2-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155629\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ravana-waterfall-2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155629\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ravana-waterfall-2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\