Best of all, it&#x2019;s only a 10-minute drive out of Ella town, so it&#x2019;s the perfect activity for an afternoon in Ella.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Entry Fee and Opening Times:<\/strong> Open 9 &#x2013; 5 every day with tickets costing 18 USD.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"ellarock\">8. Hike to the top of Ella Rock<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Wherever you are in Ella, you&#x2019;ll always feel the magnificent presence of the towering Ella Rock. The beautiful green mountain is one of the most popular hikes and one of the best things to do in Ella. What&#x2019;s unique about this hike is that the trail is incredibly natural and overgrown, giving you a real adventurous feeling.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2.jpg\" alt=\"Things to do Ella Sri Lanka Ella Rock\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"Things to do Ella Sri Lanka Ella Rock\" class=\"wp-image-6583 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-1440x961.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155701\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Ella-Rock-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The hike takes around 2 hours from Ella town to the summit, passing along train tracks through long grass fields and dense forest. Reaching the top is an incredible feeling, dangling your legs off the rock and looking down at the valley below. It&#x2019;s a good idea to start the hike as early as possible in the morning so that you can avoid the hot sun. Make sure also to pack layers as it will be cold in the early hours and much hotter as you descend.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-insurance\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Finding a Travel Insurance &#x2013; Everything to Know<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> The adventurous nature of this hike means that it can be easy to get lost. Make sure to get directions from your guesthouse manager or other travelers before you go. Don&#x2019;t forget to pack lots of snacks and water for the journey!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>9. Explore Ella Town<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The town of Ella has to be one of the most picturesque settings in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka.<\/a> Aside from the incredible nature that draws travelers from all over the world, the town has an entertaining atmosphere with great cafes and restaurants. If you&#x2019;re also looking for lively nightlife, head for one of the bars on the main street. For example, Cafe Chill serves tasty cocktails, smoothies, and a variety of cuisines and plays music into the early hours.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you happen to be in Ella on a Wednesday, the town puts on a small market in the mornings. Passara Road (Ella Super) becomes lined with small stalls selling clothing, fresh vegetables, herbs, and fruits.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-town-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6598 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155618\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-town-2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155618\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-town-2-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155618\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-town-2-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155618\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-town-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155618\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-town-2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155618\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-town-2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155618\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-town-2-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/u