e reaching beautiful Ella.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-1080x810.jpg\" alt=\"sri-lanka train ella kandy\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri-lanka train ella kandy\" class=\"wp-image-7584 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/01\/23154008\/sri-lanka-route-guide-train-ella-kandy-1440x1080.jpg 1440w, http