class=\"product__content-title\">Eden View Sri Lanka<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/raveena-guest-house\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23164007\/36776957-30x16.jpg\" alt=\"Raveena Guest House\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23164007\/36776957-450x246.jpg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">Raveena Guest House<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"besttime\">Best Time to Visit Ella<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With its warm days and cool nights, the weather in Ella, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>, is always perfect. However, the green lusciousness of the area does mean there&#x2019;s plenty of rain too, although it never lasts for long! The wet season is from September to December, so we recommend visiting in the drier months of January to May. During this time, it is busier in Ella, and the waterfalls have less water. However, it&#x2019;s excellent for hiking!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"restaurants\">Best Cafes &amp; Restaurants in Ella<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ella is a top-rated destination for travelers and, because of this, has a variety of restaurants selling different cuisines. If you want to try some beautiful local delicacies, Ella has got lovely locally run cafes. However, if you&#x2019;ve been on the backpacking trail for a while, you can also find your western favorites. Some of our top recommendations are:&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Cafe Chill<\/li><li>Jade Green Tea Center &amp; Restaurant<\/li><li>Matey Hut<\/li><li>AK Ristoro<\/li><li>Rose Cabin Mexican Restaurant<\/li><li>Adam&#x2019;s Breeze<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155709\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Chill-restaurant-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6579 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155709\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Chill-restaurant-2.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155709\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Chill-restaurant-2-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155709\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Chill-restaurant-2-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155709\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Chill-restaurant-2-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155709\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Chill-restaurant-2-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155709\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-Chill-restaurant-2-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/s